{"tid":2449112,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Xbox Series X Controller RT掣黏住 彈唔翻上嚟","createTime":"2021-03-16T11:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T02:15:14.000Z","uid":328327,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a36e45a01da437572494004a56c6792703de3ad","tid":2449112,"uid":328327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:54:19.000Z","msg":"我買咗一個月都無就有岀現呢個問題。我見網上外國好多人都同樣有岀現，包括Xbox one 手掣。<br />\n我無自己拆嚟整，寄咗上Xbox維修部，全程一個禮拜到就到翻我手，售後幾好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但整咗翻嚟居然前後面板好似岀自兩個手掣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，前面反曬光，後面啞面啲（原廠嘅質感）。然後啲膠邊位又有達零舍反光嘅位，唔識形容，總之做工睇落cheap。唔知ching們從相見唔見到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成舊嘢好似老翻咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好似唔整好過整咁。後悔了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iD08SST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiD08SST.jpg&h=44111e15&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4phMcV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4phMcV.jpg&h=32033286&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKn3GMi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKn3GMi.jpg&h=6cac5247&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32f835b8e45725593f19dc3dc78f78441d0a8ca2","tid":2449112,"uid":328327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"唉，不過手感好似重要啲，只係上嚟訴下苦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdaf42c8ee020454c8756ba3db6a631ae7e96fa","tid":2449112,"uid":50020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:42:12.000Z","msg":"其實m$好少整，多數直接換<br />\n同埋售後真係幾好"},{"pid":"61af1bf91d52ed34b102e54307bbde9944bf9a60","tid":2449112,"uid":262636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"之前換過一次、因為Bluetooth成日斷同 Y太鬆，之後返黎個手掣情況就好似你咁，但我後期自己拆開佢整就改善返個手感"},{"pid":"8677a2c5a37355b3e49080f3aca7c36f3e29cb79","tid":2449112,"uid":43987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61af1bf91d52ed34b102e54307bbde9944bf9a60","tid":2449112,"uid":262636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"之前換過一次、因為Bluetooth成日斷同 Y太鬆，之後返黎個手掣情況就好似你咁，但我後期自己拆開佢整就改善返個手感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:11:38.000Z","msg":"新firmware fix左唔會斷bluetooth，可以用Xbox accessories駁線update"},{"pid":"6f59ea9ebd7af91919acab9d3d061d92226c7551","tid":2449112,"uid":262636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8677a2c5a37355b3e49080f3aca7c36f3e29cb79","tid":2449112,"uid":43987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61af1bf91d52ed34b102e54307bbde9944bf9a60","tid":2449112,"uid":262636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"之前換過一次、因為Bluetooth成日斷同 Y太鬆，之後返黎個手掣情況就好似你咁，但我後期自己拆開佢整就改善返個手感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:11:38.000Z","msg":"新firmware fix左唔會斷bluetooth，可以用Xbox accessories駁線update"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:41:17.000Z","msg":"換左新手掣之後就無咩斷，之前重玩mafia 2 ,每十分鐘就斷一次，之後嬲嬲地插線算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa84143f5179abe76b77f3e6ba9532041563bff","tid":2449112,"uid":328327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dcdaf42c8ee020454c8756ba3db6a631ae7e96fa","tid":2449112,"uid":50020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:42:12.000Z","msg":"其實m$好少整，多數直接換<br />\n同埋售後真係幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"但係換咗啲嘅嘢比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪我唔好彩"},{"pid":"3a94efca0c97a40164c8fe0001d171f2710bd3e5","tid":2449112,"uid":328327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61af1bf91d52ed34b102e54307bbde9944bf9a60","tid":2449112,"uid":262636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:20:42.000Z","